      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know about the helplines. i’ve seen them. but they don't change the fact that my whole life was built around someone who isn't there anymore. it’s not just being sad, it’s like the air is gone. everything is just... pointless. it feels like i'm just waiting for something to happen, but nothing ever will. what am i even supposed to do with a life that doesn't feel like mine anymore?",
